Teach Alexa your voice
A voice profile enables Alexa to learn your voice, call you by name, and provide enhanced personalization.
By tapping "Continue", you agree to the Alexa Terms of User and authorize Amazon to create your voice. Your voice will eb stored in the cloud. Learn more.
<"Continue" Button>

Settings > Your Profile
Create your Personal Passcode
Your personal passcode is a code that Alexa will ask for to help protect your personal data and settings.
It does not replace smart home device codes or the voice code used for Amazon purchases.
